import { React, useEffect, useState } from 'react'; import { useSelector } from 'react-redux'; import { useLocation } from 'react-router-dom'; const PartnerDashboard = () => { const { restaurant, restaurants, user } = useSelector(state => ({ ...state })); const [restaurantDet, setRestaurantDet] = useState(restaurant || ''); const location = useLocation(); useEffect(() => { if (!restaurant) { let params = location.pathname.split('/'); setRestaurantDet(restaurants?.filter(rest => rest._id === params[2])[0]); } }, [restaurant, restaurants, user]) return (

{restaurantDet?.restaurantName}

{restaurantDet?.contact}
{restaurantDet?.email}
{restaurantDet?.restaurantAddress}, {restaurantDet?.city}, {restaurantDet?.state}, {restaurantDet?.zipCode}
{restaurantDet?.status}

Owner Details

{restaurantDet?.firstName}
{restaurantDet?.lastName}
{restaurantDet?.establishmentType}
{ restaurantDet?.outletType?.map(outlet => outlet.toLowerCase())?.join(', ') }
{ restaurantDet?.cuisinesType?.map(cuisine => cuisine.toLowerCase())?.join(', ') }
) } export default PartnerDashboard;
